#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1241
msgid ""
"<b>Add a specific path:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Type the full path of a folder here and click the button next to it to "
"include that folder in the database. This is useful for adding a path "
"directly without browsing for it."
msgstr ""
"<b>Tambahkan path tertentu:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Ketik path lengkap folder di sini dan klik tombol di sebelahnya untuk "
"menyertakan folder tersebut dalam basis data. Ini berguna untuk menambahkan "
"path secara langsung tanpa menelusurinya."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1275
msgid ""
"<b>Attempt to monitor:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, FSearch watches this folder for changes and keeps the database "
"up to date automatically, so you don't have to rescan manually.\n"
"\n"
"Monitoring isn't supported on every file system and uses a small amount of "
"system resources per watched folder. For large directory trees with many "
"files the system may run out of resources to watch them all."
msgstr ""
"<b>Coba pantau:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Jika diaktifkan, FSearch memantau perubahan pada folder ini dan secara "
"otomatis menjaga basis data tetap mutakhir, sehingga Anda tidak perlu "
"memindai ulang secara manual.\n"
"\n"
"Pemantauan tidak didukung pada setiap sistem berkas dan menggunakan sedikit "
"sumber daya sistem untuk setiap folder yang dipantau. Pada pohon direktori "
"besar dengan banyak berkas, sistem mungkin kehabisan sumber daya untuk "
"memantau semuanya."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1294
msgid ""
"<b>Scan after launch:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, this folder is rescanned every time FSearch starts, so the "
"database reflects any changes made while FSearch wasn't running."
msgstr ""
"<b>Pindai setelah peluncuran:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Jika diaktifkan, folder ini dipindai ulang setiap kali FSearch dimulai, "
"sehingga basis data mencerminkan perubahan apa pun yang dibuat saat FSearch "
"tidak berjalan."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1311
msgid ""
"<b>Stay on one file system:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, FSearch won't cross file system boundaries while scanning this "
"folder. Mounted file systems below it (e.g. external drives or network "
"shares) are skipped."
msgstr ""
"<b>Tetap pada satu sistem berkas:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Jika diaktifkan, FSearch tidak akan melintasi batas sistem berkas saat "
"memindai folder ini. Sistem berkas yang dikaitkan di bawahnya (misalnya "
"kandar eksternal atau berbagi jaringan) akan dilewati."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1328
msgid ""
"<b>Rescan every:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, this folder is rescanned automatically at the given interval. "
"Use the hours and minutes fields to set how often the rescan happens.\n"
"\n"
"This is useful for folders on file systems that can't be monitored for "
"changes."
msgstr ""
"<b>Pindai ulang setiap:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Jika diaktifkan, folder ini dipindai ulang secara otomatis pada interval "
"yang diberikan. Gunakan kolom jam dan menit untuk mengatur seberapa sering "
"pemindaian ulang dilakukan.\n"
"\n"
"Ini berguna untuk folder pada sistem berkas yang perubahannya tidak dapat "
"dipantau."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1347
msgid ""
"<b>Exclude rules:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This list contains rules for the files and folders you want to exclude from "
"the database.\n"
"\n"
"\t• <b>Active:</b> If enabled, the rule is applied and matching items are "
"excluded.\n"
"\t• <b>Pattern:</b> The text matched against each item, interpreted "
"according to the Type.\n"
"\t• <b>Type:</b> How the pattern is interpreted — <i>Literal</i> (exact "
"text), <i>Wildcard</i> (using * and ?) or <i>Regex</i> (a regular "
"expression).\n"
"\t• <b>Match:</b> Whether the pattern is matched against the item's <i>Full "
"Path</i> or only its <i>Basename</i> (the name without the path).\n"
"\t• <b>Applies To:</b> Whether the rule affects <i>Files</i>, <i>Folders</i> "
"or both."
msgstr ""
"<b>Aturan pengecualian:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Daftar ini berisi aturan untuk berkas dan folder yang ingin Anda kecualikan "
"dari basis data.\n"
"\n"
"\t• <b>Aktif:</b> Jika diaktifkan, aturan diterapkan dan butir yang cocok "
"dikecualikan.\n"
"\t• <b>Pola:</b> Teks yang dicocokkan dengan setiap butir, ditafsirkan "
"sesuai Tipe.\n"
"\t• <b>Tipe:</b> Cara pola ditafsirkan — <i>Literal</i> (teks persis), "
"<i>Wildcard</i> (menggunakan * dan ?), atau <i>Regex</i> (ekspresi "
"reguler).\n"
"\t• <b>Kecocokan:</b> Apakah pola dicocokkan dengan <i>Path Lengkap</i> "
"butir atau hanya <i>Nama Dasar</i>-nya (nama tanpa path).\n"
"\t• <b>Berlaku Untuk:</b> Apakah aturan memengaruhi <i>Berkas</i>, "
"<i>Folder</i>, atau keduanya."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1370
msgid ""
"<b>Add exclude rule:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This adds a new, empty rule to the list. Edit its Pattern, Type, Match and "
"Applies To columns to control what gets excluded from the database."
msgstr ""
"<b>Tambahkan aturan pengecualian:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Ini menambahkan aturan baru yang kosong ke daftar. Edit kolom Pola, Tipe, "
"Kecocokan, dan Berlaku Untuk untuk mengendalikan apa yang dikecualikan dari "
"basis data."

#: src/fsearch_statusbar.ui:726
msgid ""
"The search was cancelled before it finished.\n"
"<b>These results are incomplete.</b>"
msgstr ""
"Pencarian dibatalkan sebelum selesai.\n"
"<b>Hasil ini tidak lengkap.</b>"

#: src/fsearch_statusbar.ui:756
msgid "PARTIAL"
msgstr "SEBAGIAN"

#: src/fsearch_welcome_dialog.ui:26
msgid "What's New in FSearch"
msgstr "Yang Baru di FSearch"

#: src/fsearch_welcome_dialog.ui:79
msgid ""
"<span size=\"xx-large\" weight=\"bold\">What's New in FSearch 0.3</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span size=\"xx-large\" weight=\"bold\">Yang Baru di FSearch 0.3</span>"

#: src/fsearch_welcome_dialog.ui:149
msgid "<big><b>File System Monitoring</b></big>"
msgstr "<big><b>Pemantauan Sistem Berkas</b></big>"

#: src/fsearch_welcome_dialog.ui:163
msgid ""
"You can now actively watch individual folders to eliminate frequent rescans. "
"File changes then appear in your search results immediately.\n"
"\n"
"To enable this feature go to the Database section of the Preferences "
"dialog.\n"
"\n"
"See the online documentation for more information:\n"
"<a href=\"URL\">https://github.com/cboxdoerfer/fsearch/wiki/Database-update</"
"a>"
msgstr ""
"Kini Anda dapat memantau setiap folder secara aktif untuk menghilangkan "
"pemindaian ulang yang sering. Perubahan berkas kemudian langsung muncul "
"dalam hasil pencarian Anda.\n"
"\n"
"Untuk mengaktifkan fitur ini, buka bagian Basis Data pada dialog "
"Preferensi.\n"
"\n"
"Lihat dokumentasi daring untuk informasi lebih lanjut:\n"
"<a href=\"URL\">https://github.com/cboxdoerfer/fsearch/wiki/Database-update</"
"a>"

#: src/fsearch_welcome_dialog.ui:232
msgid "<big><b>Folder-Specific Rescan Schedules</b></big>"
msgstr "<big><b>Jadwal Pemindaian Ulang Khusus Folder</b></big>"

#: src/fsearch_welcome_dialog.ui:246
msgid ""
"You can now configure automatic update intervals for individual folders "
"independently and tailored to each distinct location."
msgstr ""
"Kini Anda dapat mengonfigurasi interval pembaruan otomatis untuk setiap "
"folder secara terpisah dan menyesuaikannya bagi setiap lokasi yang berbeda."

#: src/fsearch_welcome_dialog.ui:309
msgid "<big><b>Improved Exclude Rules</b></big>"
msgstr "<big><b>Aturan Pengecualian yang Disempurnakan</b></big>"

#: src/fsearch_welcome_dialog.ui:323
msgid ""
"You can now use wildcards and regular expressions to define more powerful "
"exclude rules. \n"
"Rules can be targeted specifically at files, folders, or both, and can be "
"configured to match against either the basename or the full absolute path."
msgstr ""
"Kini Anda dapat menggunakan wildcard dan ekspresi reguler untuk menentukan "
"aturan pengecualian yang lebih andal. \n"
"Aturan dapat ditargetkan secara khusus pada berkas, folder, atau keduanya, "
"serta dapat dikonfigurasi agar cocok dengan nama dasar atau path absolut "
"lengkap."

