#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:855
msgid ""
"<b>Enable dark theme:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, the system theme is asked to use a darker styling for the "
"application <i>(i.e. dark UI elements on bright text)</i>.\n"
"\n"
"Note that not all system themes provide such a darker variant, therefore "
"enabling this setting might not have an effect."
msgstr ""
"<b>Aktifkan tema gelap:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Jika diaktifkan, tema sistem diminta untuk menggunakan gaya yang lebih gelap "
"pada aplikasi <i>(yaitu elemen UI gelap dengan teks terang)</i>.\n"
"\n"
"Perlu diketahui bahwa tidak semua tema sistem menyediakan varian yang lebih "
"gelap, sehingga mengaktifkan pengaturan ini mungkin tidak berpengaruh."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:873
msgid ""
"<b>Enable client-side decorations:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, the search entry and main menu are displayed in the window title "
"bar.\n"
"\n"
"If disabled, the main menu is displayed as a menu bar with the search entry "
"below it.\n"
"This resembles a more traditional UI layout and takes a little bit more "
"space."
msgstr ""
"<b>Aktifkan dekorasi sisi klien:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Jika diaktifkan, kolom pencarian dan menu utama ditampilkan di bilah judul "
"jendela.\n"
"\n"
"Jika dinonaktifkan, menu utama ditampilkan sebagai bilah menu dengan kolom "
"pencarian di bawahnya.\n"
"Ini menyerupai tata letak UI yang lebih tradisional dan membutuhkan sedikit "
"lebih banyak ruang."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:893
msgid ""
"<b>Use binary units instead of decimal units:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This settings controls how file sizes are displayed.\n"
"\n"
"\t• <b>Binary units:</b> This refers to binary IEC prefixes <i>(e.g. 1 KiB = "
"1024 bytes)</i>\n"
"\t• <b>Decimal  units:</b> This refers to decimal SI prefixes <i>(e.g. 1 kB "
"= 1000 bytes)</i>"
msgstr ""
"<b>Gunakan satuan biner alih-alih satuan desimal:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Pengaturan ini mengontrol bagaimana ukuran file ditampilkan.\n"
"\n"
"\t-  <b>Satuan biner:</b> Mengacu pada awalan IEC biner <i>(mis. 1 KiB = "
"1024 byte)</i>\n"
"\t-  <b>Satuan desimal:</b> Mengacu pada awalan SI desimal <i>(mis. 1 kB = "
"1000 byte)</i>"

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:913
msgid ""
"<b>Remember window size:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, the window size from the previous session will be restored when "
"you open an FSearch window.\n"
"\n"
"Note that some window managers ignore this request and force the window to "
"have a different size."
msgstr ""
"<b>Ingat ukuran jendela:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Jika diaktifkan, ukuran jendela dari sesi sebelumnya akan dipulihkan saat "
"Anda membuka jendela FSearch.\n"
"\n"
"Perlu diketahui bahwa beberapa pengelola jendela mengabaikan permintaan ini "
"dan memaksa jendela memiliki ukuran yang berbeda."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:932
msgid ""
"<b>Behaviour after successfully opening a file:</b>\n"
"\n"
"When a file/folder was successfully opened one of the following actions can "
"be performed:\n"
"\t• <b>Nothing:</b> Nothing happens.\n"
"                        • <b>Minimize:</b> The currently selected FSearch "
"window becomes minimized.\n"
"\t• <b>Close:</b> Quit FSearch.\n"
"\n"
"You can configure if those actions should be triggered when the file was "
"opened with\n"
"\t• <b>keyboard shortcuts or menu entries</b> and/or\n"
"\t• <b>mouse click</b>"
msgstr ""
"<b>Perilaku setelah berhasil membuka file:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Saat file/folder berhasil dibuka, salah satu tindakan berikut dapat "
"dilakukan:\n"
"\t-  <b>Tidak ada:</b> Tidak ada yang terjadi.\n"
"                        -  <b>Minimalkan:</b> Jendela FSearch yang sedang "
"dipilih akan diminimalkan.\n"
"\t-  <b>Tutup:</b> Keluar dari FSearch.\n"
"\n"
"Anda dapat mengonfigurasi apakah tindakan tersebut harus dipicu saat file "
"dibuka dengan\n"
"\t-  <b>pintasan keyboard atau entri menu</b> dan/atau\n"
"\t-  <b>klik mouse</b>"

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:956
msgid ""
"<b>Show highlighted search terms:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, the search terms will be highlighted in the results view. For "
"example when you search for \"foo\" all appearances of <i>foo</i> in file/"
"folder names will be highlighted with bold characters:\n"
"\n"
"\t<b>foo</b>bar.txt\n"
"\tfile.<b>foo</b>\n"
"\n"
"This also works for regular expressions and wildcard expressions starting or "
"ending with an asterisk. "
msgstr ""
"<b>Tampilkan istilah pencarian yang disorot:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Jika diaktifkan, istilah pencarian akan disorot di tampilan hasil. Misalnya "
"saat Anda mencari \"foo\", semua kemunculan <i>foo</i> dalam nama file/"
"folder akan disorot dengan karakter tebal:\n"
"\n"
"\t<b>foo</b>bar.txt\n"
"\tfile.<b>foo</b>\n"
"\n"
"Ini juga berfungsi untuk ekspresi reguler dan ekspresi wildcard yang dimulai "
"atau diakhiri dengan tanda bintang. "

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:978
msgid ""
"<b>Show tooltips:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, the results view will show the full path of the focused file/"
"folder in a small tooltip window."
msgstr ""
"<b>Tampilkan tooltip:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Jika diaktifkan, tampilan hasil akan menampilkan jalur lengkap dari file/"
"folder yang difokuskan dalam jendela tooltip kecil."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:995
msgid ""
"<b>Show icons in name column:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, file/folder icons will be shown in the name column."
msgstr ""
"<b>Tampilkan ikon di kolom nama:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Jika diaktifkan, ikon file/folder akan ditampilkan di kolom nama."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1012
msgid ""
"<b>Remember column configuration:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, the column configuration of the results view from the previous "
"session will be restored when you open an FSearch window. This includes the "
"size and visibility of all columns."
msgstr ""
"<b>Ingat konfigurasi kolom:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Jika diaktifkan, konfigurasi kolom tampilan hasil dari sesi sebelumnya akan "
"dipulihkan saat Anda membuka jendela FSearch. Ini mencakup ukuran dan "
"visibilitas semua kolom."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1029
msgid ""
"<b>Remember sort order:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, the sort order of the results view from the previous session "
"will be restored when you open an FSearch window."
msgstr ""
"<b>Ingat urutan pengurutan:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Jika diaktifkan, urutan pengurutan tampilan hasil dari sesi sebelumnya akan "
"dipulihkan saat Anda membuka jendela FSearch."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1046
msgid ""
"<b>Open path with double click in path column:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, double clicking in the path column will open the selected path."
msgstr ""
"<b>Buka jalur dengan klik ganda di kolom jalur:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Jika diaktifkan, klik ganda di kolom jalur akan membuka jalur yang dipilih."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1063
msgid ""
"<b>Single click to open:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, a single click will open the selected file/folder. If you only "
"want to select a file/folder while this setting is active, you need to hold "
"<i>Ctrl</i> at the same time while clicking the file/folder."
msgstr ""
"<b>Klik sekali untuk membuka:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Jika diaktifkan, satu klik akan membuka file/folder yang dipilih. Jika Anda "
"hanya ingin memilih file/folder saat pengaturan ini aktif, Anda perlu "
"menahan <i>Ctrl</i> secara bersamaan saat mengklik file/folder tersebut."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1080
msgid ""
"<b>Show database indexing status:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, the path that is currently being indexed is displayed in the "
"statusbar."
msgstr ""
"<b>Tampilkan status pengindeksan basis data:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Jika diaktifkan, jalur yang sedang diindeks akan ditampilkan di bilah status."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1097
msgid ""
"<b>Show warning dialogs:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, a warning dialog is displayed when a file or folder failed to "
"open."
msgstr ""
"<b>Tampilkan dialog peringatan:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Jika diaktifkan, dialog peringatan akan ditampilkan saat file atau folder "
"gagal dibuka."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1114
msgid ""
"<b>Search in path when query contains path separators:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, search terms containing path separators (i.e. \"/\") will be "
"automatically matched against the full path of a file or folder."
msgstr ""
"<b>Cari di jalur jika kueri mengandung pemisah jalur:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Jika diaktifkan, istilah pencarian yang mengandung pemisah jalur (yaitu \"/"
"\") akan secara otomatis dicocokkan dengan jalur lengkap file atau folder."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1131
msgid ""
"<b>Match case when query contains at least one upper case character:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, search terms containing at least one upper case character will "
"trigger a case-sensitive search. This means a search term like <i>Foo</i> "
"will match <i>FooBar.txt</i> but not <i>foobar.txt</i>."
msgstr ""
"<b>Cocokkan huruf besar/kecil jika kueri mengandung setidaknya satu huruf "
"kapital:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Jika diaktifkan, istilah pencarian yang mengandung setidaknya satu huruf "
"kapital akan memicu pencarian yang peka huruf besar/kecil. Artinya istilah "
"pencarian seperti <i>Foo</i> akan cocok dengan <i>FooBar.txt</i> tetapi "
"tidak dengan <i>foobar.txt</i>."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1148
msgid ""
"<b>Hide results when search is empty:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, no search results are displayed when the search entry is empty.\n"
"\n"
"If disabled, all files and folders will be displayed when the search entry "
"is empty."
msgstr ""
"<b>Sembunyikan hasil saat pencarian kosong:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Jika diaktifkan, tidak ada hasil pencarian yang ditampilkan saat kolom "
"pencarian kosong.\n"
"\n"
"Jika dinonaktifkan, semua file dan folder akan ditampilkan saat kolom "
"pencarian kosong."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1167
msgid ""
"<b>Search as you type:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, the search is automatically updated with every keystroke.\n"
"\n"
"If disabled, the search is only updated when you hit <i>Enter</i> or press "
"the search button. "
msgstr ""
"<b>Cari saat mengetik:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Jika diaktifkan, pencarian secara otomatis diperbarui setiap kali tombol "
"ditekan.\n"
"\n"
"Jika dinonaktifkan, pencarian hanya diperbarui saat Anda menekan <i>Enter</"
"i> atau tombol cari. "

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1186
msgid ""
"<b>Update database on start:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, the database will be updated automatically in the background "
"when you start FSearch."
msgstr ""
"<b>Perbarui basis data saat mulai:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Jika diaktifkan, basis data akan diperbarui secara otomatis di latar "
"belakang saat Anda memulai FSearch."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1203
msgid ""
"<b>Included folders:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This list contains all folders you want to include in the database.\n"
"\n"
"\t• <b>Active:</b> If enabled, the path will included in the database to be "
"searched in.\n"
"\t• <b>Path:</b> The full path to be included.\n"
"\t• <b>One Filesystem:</b> If enabled, FSearch won't cross filesystem "
"boundaries for this folder"
msgstr ""
"<b>Folder yang disertakan:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Daftar ini berisi semua folder yang ingin Anda sertakan dalam basis data.\n"
"\n"
"\t-  <b>Aktif:</b> Jika diaktifkan, jalur akan disertakan dalam basis data "
"untuk dicari.\n"
"\t-  <b>Jalur:</b> Jalur lengkap yang akan disertakan.\n"
"\t-  <b>Satu Sistem Berkas:</b> Jika diaktifkan, FSearch tidak akan melewati "
"batas sistem berkas untuk folder ini"

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1224
msgid ""
"<b>Add folder to database:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This button opens a dialog where you can select a folder you want to include "
"in the database for searching."
msgstr ""
"<b>Tambah folder ke basis data:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Tombol ini membuka dialog tempat Anda dapat memilih folder yang ingin "
"disertakan dalam basis data untuk pencarian."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1258
msgid ""
"<b>Remove selected row:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This removes the selected folder from the list of included folders."
msgstr ""
"<b>Hapus baris yang dipilih:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Ini menghapus folder yang dipilih dari daftar folder yang disertakan."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1423
msgid ""
"<b>Exclude files and folders from database:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This is a semi-colon separated list of files (or folders) you want to "
"exclude from the database. For example <i>.git;.cache;*.swp</i> will exclude "
"all files or folders which are called either <i>.git</i> or <i>.cache</i> or "
"end with <i>.swp</i>."
msgstr ""
"<b>Kecualikan file dan folder dari basis data:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Ini adalah daftar file (atau folder) yang dipisahkan titik koma yang ingin "
"Anda kecualikan dari basis data. Misalnya <i>.git;.cache;*.swp</i> akan "
"mengecualikan semua file atau folder yang bernama <i>.git</i> atau "
"<i>.cache</i> atau berakhiran <i>.swp</i>."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1440
msgid ""
"<b>Exclude hidden files and folders:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, hidden files and folders will be excluded from the database "
"<i>(i.e. all files or folders which start with a dot character)</i>."
msgstr ""
"<b>Kecualikan file dan folder tersembunyi:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Jika diaktifkan, file dan folder tersembunyi akan dikecualikan dari basis "
"data <i>(yaitu semua file atau folder yang dimulai dengan karakter titik)</"
"i>."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1457
msgid "Focus a setting to get a detailed description of what it does."
msgstr ""
"Fokus ke suatu pengaturan untuk mendapatkan deskripsi lengkap tentang "
"fungsinya."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1470
msgid ""
"<b>Periodically update database at a specific time interval:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled and as long as FSearch is running, the database will be updated "
"periodically with the given time interval.\n"
"\n"
"If you want to update the database in the background, even when FSearch is "
"not running, you should use tools like cron or systemd timers to "
"periodically trigger the update with:\n"
"\n"
"<i><tt>fsearch --update-database</tt></i>"
msgstr ""
"<b>Perbarui basis data secara berkala pada interval waktu tertentu:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Jika diaktifkan dan selama FSearch berjalan, basis data akan diperbarui "
"secara berkala sesuai interval waktu yang ditentukan.\n"
"\n"
"Jika Anda ingin memperbarui basis data di latar belakang, bahkan saat "
"FSearch tidak berjalan, Anda harus menggunakan alat seperti cron atau "
"systemd timer untuk memicu pembaruan secara berkala dengan:\n"
"\n"
"<i><tt>fsearch --update-database</tt></i>"

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1491
msgid ""
"<b>Launch desktop files:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, activating a <i>.desktop</i> file will launch the application "
"defined within that file. This way FSearch can act like an application "
"launcher. Otherwise the <i>.desktop</i> file will be opened with the default "
"handler for this type of files, which is usually a text editor."
msgstr ""
"<b>Jalankan file desktop:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Jika diaktifkan, mengaktifkan file <i>.desktop</i> akan meluncurkan aplikasi "
"yang didefinisikan dalam file tersebut. Dengan cara ini FSearch dapat "
"berfungsi sebagai peluncur aplikasi. Jika tidak, file <i>.desktop</i> akan "
"dibuka dengan penangan bawaan untuk tipe file ini, yang biasanya adalah "
"editor teks."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1508
msgid ""
"<b>Filters:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This is a list of all available filters. A filter is a predefined search.\n"
"\n"
"\t• <b>Name:</b> A unique and descriptive identifier for the filter\n"
"\t• <b>Macro:</b> By typing the macro text followed by a ':' you can enable "
"the filter on demand\n"
"\t• <b>Query:</b> The search term by which the database should be filtered"
msgstr ""
"<b>Filter:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Ini adalah daftar semua filter yang tersedia. Filter adalah pencarian yang "
"telah ditentukan sebelumnya.\n"
"\n"
"\t-  <b>Nama:</b> Pengenal yang unik dan deskriptif untuk filter\n"
"\t-  <b>Makro:</b> Dengan mengetik teks makro diikuti ':' Anda dapat "
"mengaktifkan filter sesuai kebutuhan\n"
"\t-  <b>Kueri:</b> Istilah pencarian yang digunakan untuk memfilter basis "
"data"

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1529
msgid ""
"<b>Add a new filter:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This button opens a dialog where you can edit a new filter."
msgstr ""
"<b>Tambah filter baru:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Tombol ini membuka dialog tempat Anda dapat mengedit filter baru."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1546
msgid ""
"<b>Remove selected filter:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This button removes the currently selected filter."
msgstr ""
"<b>Hapus filter yang dipilih:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Tombol ini menghapus filter yang sedang dipilih."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1563
msgid ""
"<b>Edit selected filter:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This button opens a dialog where you can edit the selected filter."
msgstr ""
"<b>Edit filter yang dipilih:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Tombol ini membuka dialog tempat Anda dapat mengedit filter yang dipilih."

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1580
msgid ""
"<b>Restore default filters:</b>\n"
"\n"
"This button restores the default filter configuration.\n"
"\n"
"⚠ All filters which were created or edited by the user will be lost! ⚠"
msgstr ""
"<b>Pulihkan filter bawaan:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Tombol ini memulihkan konfigurasi filter bawaan.\n"
"\n"
"⚠ Semua filter yang dibuat atau diedit oleh pengguna akan hilang! ⚠"

#: src/fsearch_preferences.ui:1599
msgid ""
"<b>Exit on Escape:</b>\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, FSearch exits when the Escape key is pressed instead of the "
"window being minimized."
msgstr ""
"<b>Keluar dengan Escape:</b>\n"
"\n"
"Jika diaktifkan, FSearch keluar saat tombol Escape ditekan alih-alih jendela "
"diminimalkan."

